<l>teṉpulattār teyvam viruntokka ṟāṉeṉṟāṅ</l>
<l>kaimpulattā ṟōmpa ṟalai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The southern fathers, god, guest, family and oneself—to guard</l>
<l>the path through those five regions is the main thing.</l>
